cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

This paper deals with transfer learning in natural language processing (NLP) tasks, specifically aspect-based sentiment classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel application of expectation regularization (XR) for transfer learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method involves training a model on a large corpus, which could also fall under computer vision (cs.CV) or information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
